forms 1


copy the skeleton

1-Text field

add to the div wrapping the input and label a class of input-field

2-text area
add a class to the div wrapping the text area of: input-field
add a class of to the textarea tag: materialize-textarea

3-inline field
add a class of inline next to the input-field class. 

4-icon prefix
first div class input-field
i tag class material-icons prefix inside phone (to ge the phone icon)

5-Validation

-first div input-field
input tag a class of validate
and add a message of:
add on the label tag: data-error="Invalid" data-success="Valid"

6-Select

wrapping div class input-field 
-inside the select create 4 options
-the first one option will have attributes of: disabled selected.
Populate them with text Option 1 to 4.
-go to the jquery down and initialize the select list:
using jquery
$('select).material_select();




 


